faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個飯，係一pat野，爛晒嘅質感，屌，都唔知食緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後係個啲所謂嘅肉粒，<br />\n我覺得係似咬緊一啲纖維<br />\n係一啲肉味都無，最多得個啲咩鬆肉粉嘅味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後係個啲青豆粒蘿蔔粒，<br />\n嘩屌，一撚定係雪藏左唔知幾耐個啲<br />\n無味都算，咬落係粉粉地，容容爛爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係貪平，想好嘅又一餐，唔好嘅又一餐，填飽個肚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後成碟飯最好食係稀有到乜咁嘅粟米粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我終於食到一啲天然嘅粟米甜味啦<br />\nDLLM<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdacdae973621db7c22b9eff51da4bf874c129c7","tid":523930,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"魚肉燒賣飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8c235bf88735c2d3d5c7bebc7ca5f73a25cd9d","tid":523930,"uid":104589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a57ba4fdd91fe1bee24edeea0a107e6858ed0733","tid":523930,"uid":82561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:06:07.000Z","msg":"CityU AC1 嘅12蚊(?)頹飯<br />\n咩粟米肉粒飯<br />\n個白汁，係夠杰<br />\n但係一啲咪都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face